OL,3,CEmergency government taskforce created
OL,4,Cto tackle 'housing crisis'
OL,6,Fnew Housing Minister has officially
OL,7,Fstarted a 'Crisis Emergency Taskforce'
OL,8,Fto tackle the island's pressured
OL,9,Fproperty market, ITV News has learned.
OL,11,FDeputy Sam Mezec, who is also the
OL,12,Fleader of the Reform Jersey party, has
OL,13,Ftold his team to establish the group
OL,14,F"immediately".
OL,16,FThey are expected to meet for the
OL,17,Ffirst time on Monday 5 February.
