OL,6,FHe added: "I have also brought forward
OL,7,Fthe timeline for introducing new
OL,8,Flegislation to protect people who rent
OL,9,Ftheir homes."
OL,11,FThe Jersey Landlords' Association said
OL,12,Fthey looked forward to "working
OL,13,Fconstructively with the Minister in
OL,14,Ffuture" but pointed to a recent
OL,15,Fconsultation of more than 300 tenants
OL,16,Fand landlords as they called for a
OL,17,Fcompromise.
