OL,6,FThe Association added: "We trust that
OL,7,FDeputy Mezec will not ignore these
OL,8,Fvoices in seeking to find a balance
OL,9,Fthat is right for all stakeholders in
OL,10,FJersey's housing market."
OL,12,FThe cost of housing in the island has
OL,13,Frisen by 16.7% in the last 12 months
OL,14,Fand the latest data suggests the
OL,15,Faverage house price is #681,000,
OL,16,Fcompared to #291,000 in the UK.
