OL,4,Cto tackle 'housing crisis'
OL,6,FThe news of a government housing
OL,7,Ftaskforce comes as the new Council of
OL,8,FMinisters began their first day
OL,9,Fmeeting officials at government
OL,10,Fbuildings in Broad Street, .
OL,12,FMandy Phillips, a resident in Jersey,
OL,13,Fsays: "In the fifteen years I've lived
OL,14,Fin Jersey, I've moved house 13 or 14
OL,15,Ftimes for a variety of reasons."
OL,17,FShe added housing costs are a concern:
OL,18,F"I work full-time and I have another
OL,19,Fjob in the evening to be able to
OL,20,Fafford to pay rent.
